- Last night? - All that marching! Tramp, tramp, tramp!

832
01:18:25,117 --> 01:18:28,704
可能是军队演习吧？我再也不会邀请那些家伙了
- Army maneuvers maybe? - I'll never invite those people again.

833
01:18:28,871 --> 01:18:33,042
把房子出租给单身汉感觉好吧？整晚上都没有睡个10分钟的安稳觉
What you get from renting to bachelors. All night I didn't sleep ten minutes.

834
01:18:33,209 --> 01:18:38,714
- 我肯定你把爵福斯医生喊起来了　- 不要担心，他现在出去看病去了
- And I'm sure you woke up Dr. Dreyfuss. - Don't worry. He was out on a case.

835
01:18:38,881 --> 01:18:43,969
巴克斯特先生，我警告你：这是高级公寓，不是下等旅社。
I'm warning you, Mr. Baxter. This is a respectable house, not a honky-tonky.

836
01:18:44,136 --> 01:18:46,222
快点，奥斯卡
Come on, Oscar.

837
01:19:13,165 --> 01:19:17,795
总机，请帮我接通白色庄园的JD·舍尔爵克先生的电话
Operator, I want White Plains, New York. Mr. J.D. Sheldrake.

838
01:19:17,962 --> 01:19:20,047
记住这是一个私人电话
Make that person-to-person.

839
01:19:24,802 --> 01:19:27,805
5，4，3，2，1…
Five, four, three, two, one...

840
01:19:27,972 --> 01:19:30,516
让她全速前进
Let her rip!

841
01:19:30,683 --> 01:19:32,267
我来接电话
I'll get the phone.

842
01:19:32,434 --> 01:19:35,354
爸爸，为什么我们不在火箭这里放一只苍蝇呢
Hey, Dad, why don't we put a fly in the nose cone?

843
01:19:35,521 --> 01:19:38,399
- 如果我们能把它活着带回来的话　- 好主意
- See if we can bring it back alive. - That's a thought.

844
01:19:38,565 --> 01:19:42,611
也许我们能够放两只苍蝇，看他们能不能在太空中繁殖
Maybe we should put in two flies and see if they'll propagate in orbit.

845
01:19:42,778 --> 01:19:46,907
- 看她们能干什么？　- 繁殖啊，你知道，就是生小苍蝇
- See if they'll what? - Propagate. You know. Multiply.

846
01:19:47,074 --> 01:19:50,828
- 小苍蝇　- 呵，呵
- Baby flies? - Oh. Oh!

847
01:19:51,620 --> 01:19:54,164
- 你的电话，爸爸　- 谢谢，杰夫
- It's for you, Dad. - Thanks, Jeff.

848
01:19:54,331 --> 01:19:57,501
一个叫巴克斯特的先生，说是私人电话
A Mr. Baxter. Person-to-person.

849
01:19:57,668 --> 01:20:00,254
快点，帮我放一些苍蝇
Come on. Help me round up some flies.

850
01:20:00,421 --> 01:20:06,010
- 你好？巴克斯特先生，你脑子出问题了么？　- 发生了一些很重要的事情
- Hello? What's on your mind, Baxter? - Something came up that's important.

851
01:20:06,176 --> 01:20:09,513
我想你最好尽快赶到我的公寓和我见面
I think you should see me at the apartment as soon as possible.

852
01:20:09,680 --> 01:20:13,350
- 究竟是怎么回事？　- 我不想在电话上谈这件事情
- What's this all about? - I didn't wanna tell you over the phone.

853
01:20:13,517 --> 01:20:18,605
在晚会后，你知道我的意思，我昨天晚上在我的公寓发现她了
But that certain party... You know who I mean. I found her here last night.

854
01:20:18,772 --> 01:20:21,942
- 她服用了大量的安眠药　- 什么？
- She took an overdose of sleeping pills. - What?!

855
01:20:23,277 --> 01:20:27,239
- 杰夫，是谁啊，你和谁讲电话呢？　- 我们的一个员工出了意外
- What is it, Jeff? Who's on the phone? - One of our employees had an accident.

856
01:20:27,406 --> 01:20:30,784
我不知道为什么他们总是在圣诞节用这些事情来烦我
I don't know why they bother me with these things on Christmas Day.

857
01:20:30,951 --> 01:20:32,745
是的，巴克斯特先生
Yes, Baxter.

858
01:20:32,911 --> 01:20:35,205
情况有多严重
Just how serious is it?

859
01:20:35,372 --> 01:20:39,001
还好，危险期已经过了，但是她现在还在沉睡
It was touch and go there for a while, but she's sleeping it off now.

860
01:20:39,168 --> 01:20:42,212
我想你最好当她醒来的时候能在这里
I thought maybe you'd like to be here when she wakes up.

861
01:20:43,213 --> 01:20:47,676
那不可能，巴克斯特，你要一个人帮我搞定这件事情
That's impossible. You'll have to handle the situation yourself, Baxter.

862
01:20:47,843 --> 01:20:52,222
- 事实上，我非常相信你的能力　- 知道，先生，我明白
- As a matter of fact, I'm counting on you. - Yes, sir. I understand.

863
01:20:52,389 --> 01:20:56,727
她留下一封信，你需要我现在打开给你读信的内容吗？
She left a letter. Would you like me to open it and read it to you?

864
01:20:56,894 --> 01:20:59,563
当然，这只是一个建议
Well, it was just a suggestion.

865
01:20:59,730 --> 01:21:03,609
而且我已经把你的名字擦掉了，你不用担心
No, don't worry. I kept your name out of it, so there'll be no trouble...

866
01:21:03,776 --> 01:21:06,320
警察局或者媒体方面会有什么麻烦
...policewise or newspaperwise.

867
01:21:07,529 --> 01:21:11,867
你知道，这个医生是我的朋友，这方面你也不用太过担心
You see, the doctor is a friend of mine, so we were very lucky in that respect.

868
01:21:12,034 --> 01:21:14,536
事实上，他都以为她是我的女朋友
Actually, he thinks she's my girl.

869
01:21:15,371 --> 01:21:17,581
这只是他的错误判断
No, he just jumped to the conclusion.

870
01:21:17,748 --> 01:21:20,542
在这附近我被他们认为是一个花花公子
Around here I'm known as quite a ladies' man.

871
01:21:20,709 --> 01:21:24,922
当然，我们现在还没有完全脱离危险，有时候，他们还会找麻烦的
Of course, we're not out of the woods yet. Sometimes they try it again.

872
01:21:25,089 --> 01:21:28,926
我明白，我会尽量摆平这一切，估计她可能还要好几天才能完全康复
Yes, sir. I'll do my best. It'll take her a couple of days to fully recover...

873
01:21:29,093 --> 01:21:32,429
而且房东太太那里还会有一些麻烦
...and I may have a little problem with the landlady.

874
01:21:33,097 --> 01:21:36,558
好了，舍尔爵克先生，我会尽可能的把她留在公寓里
OK, Mr. Sheldrake. I'll keep her in the apartment as long as I can.

875
01:21:36,725 --> 01:21:40,270
你需要我给你传些什么口信吗？
Isn't there some sort of message you want me to give her?

876
01:21:40,729 --> 01:21:42,940
哦，让我想想
Well, I'll... think of something.

877
01:21:43,482 --> 01:21:45,651
好吧，再见，舍尔爵克先生
Yes, sir. Goodbye, Mr. Sheldrake.

878
01:21:48,487 --> 01:21:50,614
对不起
I'm sorry.

879
01:21:51,281 --> 01:21:54,910
- 非常抱歉，巴克斯特先生。　- 你怎么能下床乱走呢？
- I'm sorry, Mr. Baxter. - What are you doing out of bed?

880
01:21:55,077 --> 01:21:58,247
我不知道这会是你的公寓
I didn't know. I had no idea this was your apartment.

881
01:21:58,413 --> 01:22:01,125
到这里，我来帮你
Here. Let me help you.

882
01:22:01,625 --> 01:22:03,627
我没脸活下去了
Oh, I'm so ashamed.

883
01:22:03,794 --> 01:22:05,796
你为什么不让我死呢？
Why didn't you just let me die?

884
01:22:05,963 --> 01:22:11,468
这是什么话？你只是情绪有些失控，但是现在一切都过去了
What kind of talk is that? You got a little overemotional, but you're fine now.

885
01:22:11,635 --> 01:22:13,095
哦
Oh!

886
01:22:13,262 --> 01:22:17,516
我的头好痛，好想要裂了一样
Oh, my head! It feels just like a big wad of chewing gum.

887
01:22:17,683 --> 01:22:20,436
- 现在几点了？　- 2点
- What time is it? - Two o'clock.

888
01:22:20,602 --> 01:22:22,813
我的衣服到哪里去了，我现在要回家
Oh, my dress. I have to go home.

889
01:22:22,980 --> 01:22:25,399
你现在不适合到任何地方去，只能马上给我回到床上去
You're in no shape to go anywhere but back to bed.

890
01:22:25,566 --> 01:22:27,985
- 你不希望我在这里　- 怎么会呢
- You don't want me here. - Sure I do. I...

891
01:22:28,152 --> 01:22:31,280
圣诞节的时候有人做伴真好
It's always nice to have company for Christmas.

892
01:22:31,447 --> 01:22:34,950
我没事，我只想刷牙
- I'm stronger than you are. - I just wanna brush my teeth.

893
01:22:35,117 --> 01:22:38,620
哦，当然可以，我想你可以在那里找到一个新的牙刷
Oh. Of course. I think I can find a new toothbrush somewhere.

894
01:22:38,787 --> 01:22:41,498
在这里，把衣服穿上
Here. Put that on.

895
01:23:10,152 --> 01:23:13,864
- 想吃点早餐吗？　- 不，我没有胃口
- How about some breakfast? - No. I don't want anything.

896
01:23:14,031 --> 01:23:16,033
我来给你倒一些咖啡吧！
I'll fix you some coffee.

897
01:23:16,200 --> 01:23:20,496
哦，竟然都喝光了，你昨天晚上喝太多了
Oh! We're all out of coffee. You had quite a lot last night.

898
01:23:20,662 --> 01:23:22,706
我马上回来
Back in a minute.

899
01:23:32,132 --> 01:23:34,384
爵福斯太太，你能借我一些咖啡吗
Mrs. Dreyfuss, could I borrow some coffee?

900
01:23:34,551 --> 01:23:38,347
- 加一个桔子和两个鸡蛋？　- 鸡蛋，他为我要的，还有桔子！
- And an orange and a couple of eggs? - Eggs, he asks me for! Oranges!

901
01:23:38,514 --> 01:23:42,976
你现在需要好好补补身体，我老公，就是你的医生，从来都不对我隐瞒的
What you need is a good horsewhipping! From me the doctor has no secrets.

902
01:23:43,143 --> 01:23:45,354
可怜的姑娘，干什么要干这样的傻事呢
Poor girl. How could you do such a thing?

903
01:23:45,520 --> 01:23:48,523
我什么也没干，实话说，这只是…
I didn't do anything. Honest. It's just...

904
01:23:49,358 --> 01:23:54,821
你和她在一起只是为了玩乐，而她却认为你值得托付终身
You take a girl out just for laughs and she thinks you're serious marriagewise.

905
01:23:54,988 --> 01:23:58,408
大人物，对于你，我才懒的伺候你
Big shot! For you, I wouldn't lift a finger!

906
01:23:58,575 --> 01:24:01,745
但对于她，我将会准备一些东西喂她吃
But for her, I'll fix a little something to eat.

907
01:24:10,254 --> 01:24:11,922
你在和谁打电话？
Who are you calling?

908
01:24:12,089 --> 01:24:14,216
我姐姐，告诉她我发生什么事了
My sister, to tell her what happened to me.

909
01:24:14,383 --> 01:24:19,388
等一下，我们先来谈一谈，你打算告诉她什么？
Wait a minute! Let's talk it over first. Just what are you gonna tell her?

910
01:24:20,097 --> 01:24:24,059
- 我还没有太明确的打算　- 好的，你最好想清楚一些
- I haven't figured it out exactly. - Well, you'd better figure it out exactly.

911
01:24:24,226 --> 01:24:27,271
假设她问你昨天晚上为什么不回家，你会怎么回答？
Suppose she asks you why you didn't come home last night.

912
01:24:27,437 --> 01:24:29,356
我会说陪一个朋友
I'll say I spent the night with a friend.

913
01:24:29,523 --> 01:24:31,525
- 谁？　- 公司的同事
- Who? - Someone from the office.

914
01:24:31,692 --> 01:24:33,443
- 你现在在哪里？　- 在他的公寓
- Where are you now? - In his apartment.

915
01:24:33,610 --> 01:24:35,946
- 他的公寓　- 在她的公寓
- In his apartment? - In her apartment.

916
01:24:36,113 --> 01:24:38,282
- 你朋友叫什么名字？　- 巴克斯特
- What's your friend's name? - Baxter.

917
01:24:38,448 --> 01:24:41,535
- 她姓什么？　- 不记得了
- What's her first name? - Miss.

918
01:24:41,702 --> 01:24:44,454
- 你什么时候回家　- 直到我能走路为止
- When are you comin' home? - As soon as I can walk.

919
01:24:44,621 --> 01:24:46,623
- 你的腿受伤了吗？　- 不是，是我的胃不舒服
- Your legs hurt? - No, my stomach.

920
01:24:46,790 --> 01:24:49,584
- 你的胃？　- 他们一定会盘问到底的
- Your stomach? - They had to pump it out!

921
01:24:49,751 --> 01:24:54,631
你现在不能给任何人打电话，直到你完全清醒为止
You shouldn't call anybody. Not till you get the chewing gum out of your head.

922
01:24:54,798 --> 01:24:57,926
他们会担心我的，可能会报警的
They'll be worried about me. They might call the police.

923
01:24:58,093 --> 01:25:01,263
我们必须要非常小心，我们不想牵连任何人
We have to be careful. We don't wanna involve anybody.

924
01:25:01,430 --> 01:25:04,516
毕竟，舍尔爵克先生已经结婚了
After all, Mr. Sheldrake's a married man.

925
01:25:05,309 --> 01:25:07,436
谢谢提醒我
Thanks for reminding me!

926
01:25:11,148 --> 01:25:13,150
我不是这个意思
I didn't mean it that way.

927
01:25:13,317 --> 01:25:17,446
我刚才和他通过电话，他非常关心你
I was just talking to him on the phone. He's very concerned about you.

928
01:25:17,613 --> 01:25:20,324
他没有骂我吗？
He doesn't give a damn about me.

929
01:25:20,490 --> 01:25:24,161
你错了，他告诉我一一他这个大骗子
- You're wrong. He told me... - He's a liar.

930
01:25:24,328 --> 01:25:26,580
这根本不算是最坏的情形
But that's not the worst part.

931
01:25:26,747 --> 01:25:29,166
最糟糕的是我还爱他
The worst part is I still love him.

932
01:25:30,000 --> 01:25:32,127
哦，肯定是爵福斯夫人过来了

933
01:25:33,170 --> 01:25:35,330
Oh. That must be Mrs. Dreyfuss.

934
01:25:35,505 --> 01:25:39,009
记得昨天晚上来的医生吗？她是他的妻子
Remember the doctor from last night? That's his wife.

935
01:25:40,677 --> 01:25:42,763
我们的受害人在哪里呢？
So where's the victim?

936
01:25:43,764 --> 01:25:45,849
拿看刀
Max the Knife!

937
01:25:48,435 --> 01:25:52,648
- 呃，小姐，今天感觉如何？　- 我不知道，只是有一些晕
- Nu, little lady, how are we feeling today? - I don't know. Kind of dizzy.

938
01:25:52,814 --> 01:25:58,153
治头晕最好的办法就是鸡汤肉丝面，再来一杯茶
The best thing for dizzy is noodle soup with chicken white meat and a glass tea.

939
01:25:58,320 --> 01:26:02,699
- 不用，谢谢，我真的不饿　- 快吃点，对你身体很好的
- No, thank you. I'm really not hungry. - Go ahead, eat. Enjoy.

940
01:26:02,866 --> 01:26:05,786
你不会把这东西当餐巾吧？
You wouldn't have such a thing as a napkin, would you?

941
01:26:05,952 --> 01:26:09,122
- 我有一些纸巾　- 不像话，真是垮掉的一代
- I have some paper towels. - Beatnik.

942
01:26:09,289 --> 01:26:12,709
在我的厨房，第三格，餐巾就放在银餐具下面
In my kitchen, third drawer, under the good silver, are napkins.

943
01:26:12,876 --> 01:26:14,211
好的，爵福斯太太
Yes, Mrs. Dreyfuss.

944
01:26:14,378 --> 01:26:17,005
那你还等什么呢？看戏呢？
So, what are you waiting for? A singing commercial?

945
01:26:17,172 --> 01:26:19,174
- 我吃不下　- 你必须吃一点
- I can't eat. - You must eat.

946
01:26:19,341 --> 01:26:22,427
你必须好起来，忘记这个薄情寡义的家伙
And you must get healthy and you must forget him.

947
01:26:22,594 --> 01:26:25,889
当他第一次搬进来的时候，我觉得他还是一个好小伙子
Such a fine boy he seemed when he first moved in here.

948
01:26:26,056 --> 01:26:29,017
整洁干练，一个前途无量的大学生
Clean and cut, a regular lvy Leaguer.

949
01:26:29,184 --> 01:26:33,563
结果他却是一个喜欢喝酒、跳恰恰舞的毫无品位
Turns out he's King Farouk, with the drinking, with the cha-cha.

950
01:26:33,730 --> 01:26:35,732
还没有餐巾
With the no napkins.

951
01:26:35,899 --> 01:26:39,903
象你这样的一个女孩，你愿意让你的后半生充满悲伤吗？
A girl like you, for the rest of your life you wanna cry in your noodle soup?

952
01:26:40,070 --> 01:26:42,656
谁会需要呢？你现在听我说
Who needs it? Now you listen to me.

953
01:26:42,823 --> 01:26:46,910
你肯定会找到一个非常好的很有潜力的男人，或者一个钻石王老五
You'll find yourself a nice, substantial man... a widower, maybe...

954
01:26:47,077 --> 01:26:50,747
成立一个幸福美满的家庭，而不是吃安眠药
...and settle down, instead of noshing all those sleeping pills.

955
01:26:50,914 --> 01:26:54,042
为什么？为谁呢？为一些喜欢社交与享乐的人？
For what? For whom? For some good-time Charlie?

956
01:26:56,539 --> 01:26:59,086
餐巾拿到了，我们喝些香槟如何
One napkin comin' up. Wish we had some champagne to wrap it around.

957
01:27:00,424 --> 01:27:03,552
- 我告诉你什么了？　- 爵福斯太太，你不需要在这里等
- What did I tell you? - Mrs. Dreyfuss, you don't have to wait.

958
01:27:03,718 --> 01:27:07,597
我要回去洗碗去了，你现在休息一下，这些东西等我回来拿
- I'll wash the dishes. - You'd break 'em. I'll come back for them.

959
01:27:07,764 --> 01:27:10,350
如果他欺负你，就叫我一声
If he makes trouble, give me a yell.

960
01:27:11,601 --> 01:27:15,439
- 她好像不太喜欢你啊　- 哦，没关系，我不在乎
- She doesn't seem to like you very much. - Oh, I don't mind.

961
01:27:15,605 --> 01:27:18,108
实际上，我反而觉得受宠若惊
As a matter of fact, I'm sort of flattered.

962
01:27:18,275 --> 01:27:23,488
他们都认为象你这样的女孩会为了象我这样的人做这样的傻事
That anybody'd think a girl like you would do a thing like this over a guy like me.

963
01:27:24,698 --> 01:27:27,743
你看到这里的东西没有？一个信封？
Did you find something here? An envelope?

964
01:27:27,909 --> 01:27:29,453
是的，在我这里
Yes. I've got it.

965
01:27:29,619 --> 01:27:33,957
你觉得我们是不是最好把它销毁，这样就不会给别人抓到把柄
Don't you think we'd better destroy it so it won't fall in the wrong hands?

966
01:27:34,124 --> 01:27:36,209
打开
Open it.

967
01:27:39,796 --> 01:27:42,382
这里什么也没有，就只有100美元
There's nothing here but a $100 bill.

968
01:27:42,549 --> 01:27:45,969
是的，你是不是想让舍尔爵克拿到这东西
That's right. Will you see that Mr. Sheldrake gets it?

969
01:27:47,095 --> 01:27:49,139
当然
Sure.

970
01:27:50,640 --> 01:27:52,726
把这拿开，好吗？
Take this away, will you?

971
01:27:53,393 --> 01:27:56,188
想不想看电视？要不我把它移过来
Would you like me to move the television set in here?

972
01:27:56,354 --> 01:27:59,107
- 你会玩拉米纸牌吗？　- 不太会
- You play gin rummy? - I'm not very good at it.

973
01:27:59,274 --> 01:28:03,236
- 我会，我们来玩牌吧！　- 你不用陪我玩的
- I am. Let me get the cards. - You don't have to entertain me.

974
01:28:03,403 --> 01:28:07,115
你知道的，这里没有什么可以让我们两个人一起玩的东西
There's nothing I'd like better. You know. Togetherness.

975
01:28:07,282 --> 01:28:11,953
猜猜上一个圣诞节我干什么，吃自助晚餐，逛逛动物园
Guess what I did last Christmas. Had dinner at the automat, went to the zoo...

976
01:28:12,120 --> 01:28:14,831
然后回家，在艾其伯格走了以后打扫卫生
...then came home and cleaned up after Mr. Eichelberger.

977
01:28:14,998 --> 01:28:17,334
他在这里开了一个蛋酒晚会
He had a little eggnog party here.

978
01:28:17,501 --> 01:28:19,795
所以今年我就一个人清清静静的过
So I'm way ahead this year.

979
01:28:19,961 --> 01:28:22,672
3叉，两个黑桃？
Three across. Spades double?

980
01:28:22,839 --> 01:28:24,883
好牌
High deals.

981
01:28:25,509 --> 01:28:27,636
6？8.
Six? Eight.

982
01:28:35,602 --> 01:28:38,522
我想你要彻底放弃了.
I think I'm gonna give it all up.

983
01:28:39,689 --> 01:28:41,525
放弃什么？
Give what up?

984
01:28:44,528 --> 01:28:47,531
为什么人们必须相爱呢？
Why do people have to love people, anyway?

985
01:28:48,949 --> 01:28:51,034
我知道你的意思。
I know what you mean.

986
01:28:54,204 --> 01:28:56,331
皇后(Q)
Queen.

987
01:28:59,042 --> 01:29:01,545
- 我也不想这样　- 快拿一张牌
- I don't want it. - Pick a card.

988
01:29:06,341 --> 01:29:10,679
你认为一个人在出车祸的时候，还是糊里糊涂应该算什么？
What do you call it when somebody keeps gettin' smashed up in car accidents?

989
01:29:10,845 --> 01:29:14,182
- 恶意索赔的危险？　- 那是我和男人
- Bad insurance risk? - That's me with men.

990
01:29:15,809 --> 01:29:20,564
人家都说我是白虎星。我的初吻是在一个墓地里发生的.
I was jinxed from the word go. First time I was ever kissed was in a cemetery.

991
01:29:20,730 --> 01:29:22,816
墓地里？
A cemetery?

992
01:29:22,983 --> 01:29:25,694
那时我15岁，喜欢到那里躲着抽烟
I was 15. We used to go there to smoke.

993
01:29:25,860 --> 01:29:30,031
他叫乔治，后来为了一个鼓队长把我甩了
His name was George and he threw me over for a drum majorette.

994
01:29:31,408 --> 01:29:33,535
Uh，gin.
Uh, gin.

995
01:29:36,913 --> 01:29:42,168
10，20…36，再加上25就是61还有两盒
That's 10, 20... 36. And 25 makes 61 and two boxes.

996
01:29:42,335 --> 01:29:44,379
我总是容易陷入情网
I have this talent for falling in love...

997
01:29:44,546 --> 01:29:48,049
但总是在错误的时间、错误的地点爱上不该爱的人
...with the wrong guy in the wrong place at the wrong time.

998
01:29:48,758 --> 01:29:50,927
哦，那你总共爱上了几个人？
Well, how many guys were there?

999
01:29:52,095 --> 01:29:53,930
三个
Three.

1000
01:29:54,097 --> 01:29:58,018
最近的一个是公司的财务经理，后来被遣送回匹茨伯格的老家
The last one was the manager of a finance company back home in Pittsburgh.

1001
01:29:58,184 --> 01:30:00,186
他们发现他的账目有巨大的差异
They found a shortage in his accounts.

1002
01:30:00,353 --> 01:30:04,107
他让我等他，他是1965年走的
He asked me to wait for him. He'll be out in 1965.

1003
01:30:05,609 --> 01:30:07,736
切牌
Cut.

1004
01:30:08,361 --> 01:30:13,408
于是我返回纽约并和我的姐姐，姐夫住在一起，他是出租车司机.
So I came to New York and moved in with my sister and her husband, a cab driver.

1005
01:30:13,575 --> 01:30:18,413
他们送我读了一个秘书学校，然后我在联合生活保险申请了一份工作
They sent me to secretarial school and then I applied for a job at Consolidated.

1006
01:30:18,580 --> 01:30:20,749
但是我的打字考试不及格
But I flunked the typing test.

1007
01:30:20,915 --> 01:30:23,627
- 太慢了？　- 不是，我打得飞快
- Too slow? - No. I can type up a storm.

1008
01:30:23,793 --> 01:30:25,921
我不会写字
I just can't spell.

1009
01:30:26,921 --> 01:30:31,968
于是他们给我一双白手套，把我安置在电梯里
So they gave me a pair of white gloves and stuck me in an elevator.

1010
01:30:32,135 --> 01:30:34,638
于是我碰到了杰夫
And that's how I met Jeff.

1011
01:30:35,805 --> 01:30:38,433
天啊，于是我被他缠上了
Oh God, I'm so fouled up.

1012
01:30:38,600 --> 01:30:41,061
现在我能做什么呢？
What am I gonna do now?

1013
01:30:43,188 --> 01:30:45,482
我又赢了你一手牌，你进展太快了
Better win a hand. You're on a blitz.

1014
01:30:47,067 --> 01:30:49,903
当你告诉他的时候，他是不是非常的难过？
Was he very upset when you told him?

1015
01:30:50,070 --> 01:30:52,155
舍尔爵克先生？是的，非常的心烦意乱
Mr. Sheldrake? Yeah, very.

1016
01:30:53,406 --> 01:30:57,077
也许他确实爱我，只是没有告诉他夫人的勇气
Maybe he does love me, only he doesn't have the nerve to tell his wife.

1017
01:30:57,243 --> 01:30:58,662
我想也是的
I'm sure that's it.

1018
01:30:58,828 --> 01:31:02,207
- 你真的这么想？　- 毫无疑问
- You really think so? - No doubt about it.

1019
01:31:03,625 --> 01:31:05,835
你能递给我那本便笺和铅笔吗？
Would you hand me that pad and pencil?

1020
01:31:06,002 --> 01:31:09,005
- 干什么用？　- 我想给舍尔爵克太太写信
- What for? - I'm gonna write to Mrs. Sheldrake.

1021
01:31:09,172 --> 01:31:11,508
- 写什么内容？　- 一个女人给另外一个女人写信
- You what? - As one woman to another.

1022
01:31:11,675 --> 01:31:15,595
- 我想她应该能理解我　- 我不认为这是一个非常好的主意
- I'm sure she'll understand. - I don't think that's a very good idea.

1023
01:31:15,762 --> 01:31:19,140
- 为什么呢？　- 首先，你不会写字
- Why not? - For one thing, you can't spell.

1024
01:31:19,307 --> 01:31:23,478
其次，如果你做了这样的事情，你会恨你自己的
Secondly, if you did something like that, you'd hate yourself.

1025
01:31:24,604 --> 01:31:27,315
我确实对我自己不满意
I don't like myself very much anyway.

1026
01:31:29,192 --> 01:31:31,611
把牌收起来，我们走！
Pick up the cards. Let's go.

1027
01:31:31,778 --> 01:31:34,864
- 我也要去吗？　- 你说对了，我手上的牌太好了
- Do I have to? - You bet. I got a terrific hand.

1028
01:31:41,621 --> 01:31:44,457
- 你要把牌全扔了吗？　- 当然
- You really wanna discard that? - Sure.

1029
01:31:44,624 --> 01:31:46,501
Gin.
Gin.

1030
01:31:49,170 --> 01:31:50,630
10，20，40，52再加上25就等于77

1031
01:31:50,790 --> 01:31:55,800
10, 20, 40, 52 and 25... 77.

1032
01:31:56,511 --> 01:32:00,015
方片翻倍就是154
Spades are double... 154.

1033
01:32:05,145 --> 01:32:07,230
哈哈，我赢了两盘了了
Blitzed. Two games.

1034
01:33:08,458 --> 01:33:10,752
好的，好的，爵福斯太太

1035
01:33:37,320 --> 01:33:40,650
All right, all right, Mrs. Dreyfuss.

1036
01:33:48,498 --> 01:33:50,291
- 嘿，巴克斯特　- 你要干什么？
- Hi, Baxter. - What do you want?

1037
01:33:50,458 --> 01:33:52,460
没事，你们等一会
What do I want? Just a minute.

1038
01:33:52,627 --> 01:33:55,255
- 你们不能进来　- 你怎么了？
- You can't come in! - What's the matter with you?

1039
01:33:55,421 --> 01:33:57,465
我预订了四点钟的房间啊
I made a reservation for four o'clock.

1040
01:33:57,632 --> 01:33:59,884
今天你不能呆在这里，拿着你的香槟快离开这里
You can't stay. Take your champagne and go.

1041
01:34:00,051 --> 01:34:03,555
我不想拿我的职位来压你，但是我已经告诉那位女士一切都搞定了
I don't wanna pull rank on you, but I told the little lady it was all set.

1042
01:34:03,721 --> 01:34:07,517
科克比先生，你是自己离开，还是让我把你扔出去
Are you gonna leave, Mr. Kirkeby, or do I have to throw you out?

1043
01:34:08,393 --> 01:34:11,145
哥们儿，不要这样说话嘛！
Buddy-boy, why didn't you say so?

1044
01:34:11,312 --> 01:34:14,482
- 你是不是也找了一个女伴？　- 现在你还不准备出去吗？
- Got yourself a little playmate, huh? - Now will you get out?

1045
01:34:14,649 --> 01:34:16,693
嘿，快点，我们还等什么呢？开门，好不好？

1046
01:34:20,150 --> 01:34:23,490
Hey, come on! What are we waiting for? Open up, will you?

1047
01:34:23,658 --> 01:34:25,702
米尔德里德！
Mildred!

1048
01:34:27,287 --> 01:34:31,708
- 为什么要这样处理呢？　- 听着，我们四个人一起开一个聚会，好吗？
- What's holding things up? - Say, let's have a party, the four of us.

1049
01:34:31,875 --> 01:34:33,960
不行
No!

1050
01:34:38,131 --> 01:34:40,383
好了，我也不想责怪你
Well, I don't blame you.

1051
01:34:40,550 --> 01:34:43,553
小伙子，这回你中头奖了？我是说和你和库伯利克
So you hit the jackpot, eh, kid? I mean Kubelikwise.

1052
01:34:43,720 --> 01:34:46,222
不要担心，我不会向其他人说的
Don't worry. I won't say a word to anybody.

1053
01:34:46,556 --> 01:34:48,641
待在这里，小伙子
Stay with it, Buddy-boy.

1054
01:35:03,698 --> 01:35:05,742
开始是谁在敲门？
Who was that?

1055
01:35:06,409 --> 01:35:09,996
哦，有人来送香槟！
Just somebody delivering a bottle of champagne. Like some?

1056
01:35:10,788 --> 01:35:13,541
你介意打开窗户吗？
Would you mind opening that window?

1057
01:35:16,252 --> 01:35:21,591
- 库伯利科小姐，不要有什么傻念头　- 我不过想透透气而已
- Now don't get any ideas, Miss Kubelik. - I just want some fresh air.

1058
01:35:21,758 --> 01:35:25,094
这里只有一层楼高，你充其量只会摔断一条腿
It's only one storey down. The best you could do is break a leg.

1059
01:35:25,261 --> 01:35:28,014
他们会痛扁我一顿的
So they'll shoot me, like a horse.

1060
01:35:28,264 --> 01:35:31,601
你要答应我你不会做任何的傻事
Please, you gotta promise me you won't do anything foolish.

1061
01:35:31,768 --> 01:35:34,270
- 谁会在乎我呢　- 我会
- Who'd care? - I would.

1062
01:35:40,026 --> 01:35:43,947
为什么我没有爱上你这样的好人呢？
Why can't I ever fall in love with somebody nice like you?

1063
01:35:44,864 --> 01:35:46,950
好的
Yeah. Well...

1064
01:35:47,575 --> 01:35:50,578
这是崩溃的好办法，就像捏碎小甜饼一样
That's the way it crumbles, cookiewise.

1065
01:35:51,913 --> 01:35:54,415
睡一会儿吧
Go to sleep.

1066
01:36:28,491 --> 01:36:33,329
- 早上好，舍尔爵克先生　- 奥尔森小姐，请到我的办公室来一下
- Good morning, Mr. Sheldrake. - Miss Olsen, come into my office, please.

1067
01:36:42,672 --> 01:36:46,634
- 圣诞节过的怎么样？　- 托您的福，很不错
- Did you have a nice Christmas? - Lovely. You were a great help!

1068
01:36:46,801 --> 01:36:49,429
你在公司晚会和库伯利克小姐说了什么？
Your pep talk to Miss Kubelik at the office party.

1069
01:36:49,595 --> 01:36:54,183
- 不好意思，杰夫，我想我可能喝多了　- 我想你应该管好你的嘴
- Sorry, Jeff. I never could hold my liquor. - I thought you could hold your tongue.

1070
01:36:54,350 --> 01:36:56,853
- 我保证再也不会这样了　- 你确实再也不会了
- It won't happen again. - You bet it won't.

1071
01:36:57,020 --> 01:36:59,939
我会安排给你发一个月工资
I'll arrange for you to get a month's severance pay.

1072
01:37:00,106 --> 01:37:03,151
好的，奥尔森小姐，我现在放你长假了
That's right, Miss Olsen. I'm letting you go.

1073
01:37:03,860 --> 01:37:06,362
杰夫，你四年前就已经抛弃我一次了
You let me go four years ago, Jeff.

1074
01:37:06,529 --> 01:37:10,950
还那么残忍让我坐在外面，看着你一个又一个的新情人来来去去
And were cruel enough to make me sit out there and watch the new models pass by.

1075
01:37:11,117 --> 01:37:14,203
我希望你能够马上从我面前消失
I'd appreciate it if you'd be out of here as soon as you can.

1076
01:37:14,370 --> 01:37:16,497
好的，舍尔爵克先生
Yes, Mr. Sheldrake.

1077
01:37:25,214 --> 01:37:29,385
总机，我是舍尔爵克先生，请帮我查一下巴克斯特先生家里的电话
Operator, this is Mr. Sheldrake. I'd like Mr. Baxter's home telephone number.

1078
01:37:29,552 --> 01:37:32,513
他在普通保险清算部
He's in Ordinary Premium Accounting.

1079
01:37:48,738 --> 01:37:52,408
喂？喂，杰夫·舍尔爵克，你现在方便讲话吗？
- Hello? - Hello. Jeff Sheldrake. Can you talk?

1080
01:37:53,076 --> 01:37:54,911
可以，她现在正在洗澡
Yes. She's in the shower.

1081
01:37:55,078 --> 01:37:57,747
- 现在她一切都还好　- 好的
- She's coming along fine, considering. - Good.

1082
01:37:57,914 --> 01:38:01,501
- 你需要什么？钱吗？　- 不用，谢谢，舍尔爵克先生
- Is there anything you need? Money? - No, thank you, Mr. Sheldrake.

1083
01:38:01,667 --> 01:38:04,796
事实上，我这里还有你的100美元
As a matter of fact, I have some money for you. $100.

1084
01:38:04,962 --> 01:38:06,339
噢！
Oh.

1085
01:38:06,506 --> 01:38:10,301
- 这里还有什么需要我帮你的吗？　- 为我？我想不用了
- If there's anything I can do for you... - For me? I don't think so.

1086
01:38:10,468 --> 01:38:13,262
但是我真的希望你能为她做一些事情
But I was hoping maybe you could do something for her.

1087
01:38:13,513 --> 01:38:16,849
比如说呢？巴克斯特，你设身处地的为我想想
Like what? Put yourself in my place, Baxter.

1088
01:38:17,016 --> 01:38:19,268
我现在怎么能帮她呢？我现在很忙
How can I help her? My hands are tied.

1089
01:38:20,520 --> 01:38:23,022
这样啊，至少你应该和她通通电话
Well... at least you can talk to her.

1090
01:38:24,107 --> 01:38:27,735
你等我让她穿好衣服，请你对她温柔点
Let me put her on. And please, be gentle.

1091
01:38:28,403 --> 01:38:30,863
电话打给你的
There's a call for you!

1092
01:38:31,030 --> 01:38:33,533
- 给我？　- 是，舍尔爵克先生。
- For me? - Yeah. Mr. Sheldrake.

1093
01:38:35,451 --> 01:38:37,453
我不想和他说话
I don't wanna talk to him.

1094
01:38:37,620 --> 01:38:39,539
我想你应该和他说说
I think you should.

1095
01:38:39,705 --> 01:38:45,086
我要去下面的杂货店一趟，除了冰冻匹萨我这里什么都没有了
I gotta run down to the grocery anyway. There's nothing left here but frozen pizza.

1096
01:38:45,878 --> 01:38:47,964
我很快就回来，好吗？
I'll be right back. OK?

1097
01:39:08,401 --> 01:39:10,486
喂，杰夫
Hello, Jeff.

1098
01:39:11,904 --> 01:39:15,032
- 我一切都好　- 弗兰，为什么做这种傻事呢？
- Yes, I'm all right. - Why did you do it, Fran?

1099
01:39:15,199 --> 01:39:17,660
你太孩子气了，这解决不了任何问题的
It's so childish, and it never solves anything.

1100
01:39:17,827 --> 01:39:20,496
你这个样子吓死我了，我都要气死了
I oughta be very angry with you, scaring me that way.

1101
01:39:20,663 --> 01:39:25,376
让我们忘记这一切，就当没发生过你觉得怎么样？
But let's forget the whole thing, pretend it never happened. What do you say?

1102
01:39:25,543 --> 01:39:27,670
弗兰？
Fran?

1103
01:39:28,045 --> 01:39:30,673
弗兰，你还在吗？
Are you there, Fran?

1104
01:39:32,091 --> 01:39:36,554
我当然不在这里，整件事情也没有发生
Of course I'm not here, because the whole thing never happened.

1105
01:39:36,721 --> 01:39:40,558
我从来没有吃过安眠药，从来没有爱过你
I never took those pills, I never loved you...

1106
01:39:40,725 --> 01:39:43,019
我们从来也没有相遇
...we never even met.

1107
01:39:44,187 --> 01:39:48,191
- 杰夫，这样你是不是满意了？　- 你知道我不是这个意思的
- Isn't that the way you want it, Jeff? - You know I didn't mean it that way.

1108
01:39:48,357 --> 01:39:51,110
你好好养身体吧，按照看护的话去做，我是指巴克斯特
You just get well. Do what the nurse says. I mean Baxter.

1109
01:39:51,277 --> 01:39:54,405
我会尽快去看你的，再见，弗兰
I'll see you as soon as I can. Goodbye, Fran.

1110
01:40:12,715 --> 01:40:15,259
喂，是舍尔爵克夫人吗？我是奥尔森小姐
Hello, Mrs. Sheldrake. This is Miss Olsen.

1111
01:40:15,426 --> 01:40:19,639
我很好，谢谢，我想我们是不是可以共进午餐
Fine, thank you. I was wondering if we could have lunch together.

1112
01:40:20,473 --> 01:40:24,143
我不知道这件事情有多严重，但是你会觉得对你有用的
I don't know how important it is, but you might find it educational.

1113
01:40:24,310 --> 01:40:26,979
是关于你丈夫的事情
It concerns your husband.

1114
01:40:27,146 --> 01:40:30,900
好的，1点钟在曼德森餐馆，品味厅59号见
All right. One o'clock, Longchamps, Madison and 59th.

1115
01:40:37,156 --> 01:40:39,408
不要担心，我马上就走
Don't worry. I'm on my way.

1116
01:40:39,575 --> 01:40:41,619
只是打一个私人电话
Just making a personal call.

1117
01:40:43,287 --> 01:40:45,373
这是一毛钱
Here's a dime.

1118
01:40:48,125 --> 01:40:49,752
快离开
Going down.

1119
01:41:02,098 --> 01:41:04,642
哦，巴克斯特先生，你还在这里
Oh, Mr. Baxter! I'm glad you're here.

1120
01:41:04,809 --> 01:41:07,436
- 我还正准备去拿备用钥匙呢？　- 干什么用？
- I was just going to get the passkey. - What for?

1121
01:41:07,603 --> 01:41:10,356
好像你的公寓里有煤气味道传出来
I thought I smelled gas coming from your apartment.

1122
01:41:10,523 --> 01:41:12,608
煤气？！
Gas?!

1123
01:41:21,659 --> 01:41:23,786
库伯利克小姐！
Miss Kubelik?

1124
01:41:25,621 --> 01:41:27,665
库伯利克小姐！
Miss Kubelik!

1125
01:41:30,334 --> 01:41:32,461
- 你还好吗？　- 当然
- You all right? - Sure!

1126
01:41:33,296 --> 01:41:36,465
- 那这煤气味是怎么回事？　- 煤气！你没有打开吗？
- What's that funny smell? - Gas! Didn't you turn it on?

1127
01:41:36,632 --> 01:41:39,552
打开了，我想烧水洗掉我衣服上的咖啡渍
Yes, to boil water to get the coffee stains out of my dress.

1128
01:41:39,719 --> 01:41:43,139
- 你把煤气打开了，但是没有点火　- 你想干什么？
- You turned it on but you didn't light it. - Are you supposed to?

1129
01:41:43,306 --> 01:41:47,059
在这间房子干什么？嘿，你在干什么呢？
In this house you're supposed to. Hey, what are you doing with that?

1130
01:41:47,226 --> 01:41:50,646
我在洗我的袜子，于是顺便把你的也洗了
I was washing my stockings, so I thought I'd wash your socks too.

1131
01:41:50,813 --> 01:41:54,942
- 哦，谢谢！　- 我很好奇，我怎么只能找到3只袜子？
- Oh. Thank you. - Very curious. I could only find 3 1/2 pair.

1132
01:41:55,109 --> 01:41:57,612
我这里有些乱糟糟的
Things are a little disorganized around here.

1133
01:41:57,778 --> 01:42:01,574
我还想问一下，为什么你的厨房有一只网球拍呢
I'd say. What's a tennis racket doing in the kitchen?

1134
01:42:01,741 --> 01:42:06,662
网球拍？哦，我想起来了，那是我自己做意大利餐的工具
Tennis racket? Oh, I remember. I was cooking myself an Italian dinner.

1135
01:42:06,829 --> 01:42:09,498
我用它来处理意大利面条
I used it to strain the spaghetti.

1136
01:42:09,665 --> 01:42:12,209
- 是这样啊　- 事实上，我是一个很好的厨师
- Why not? - In fact, I'm a pretty good cook.

1137
01:42:12,376 --> 01:42:15,171
- 但是在整理家务上面非常糟糕　- 嗯，确实如此
- Only I'm a lousy housekeeper. - Yes, you are.

1138
01:42:15,338 --> 01:42:19,675
当我整理沙发的时候，我发现了6个发夹，一支口红
When I was straightening up the couch, I found six hairpins, a lipstick...

1139
01:42:19,842 --> 01:42:23,512
一对假眼睫毛，还有斯多克俱乐部的鸡尾酒调酒棒
...a pair of false eyelashes and a swizzle stick from the Stork Club.

1140
01:42:23,679 --> 01:42:26,932
这只是因为我对任何人都不拒绝的后果
It's just that I'm the kind of guy who can't say no.

1141
01:42:27,099 --> 01:42:31,187
我不是指对女孩，我的意思是对像舍尔爵克先生一样的人
- I don't mean to girls. I mean... - To someone like Mr. Sheldrake.

1142
01:42:31,354 --> 01:42:34,440
- 我猜也是的　- 我知道
- I guess so. - I know so.

1143
01:42:36,108 --> 01:42:38,611
- 他是一个情场猎手　- 什么？
- He's a taker. - What?

1144
01:42:39,195 --> 01:42:41,364
一些人捕猎，一些人被猎
Some people take, some people get took.

1145
01:42:41,530 --> 01:42:45,534
他们知道他们需要什么类型的，而且他们并不需要做什么
And they know they're gettin' took and there's nothin' they can do about it.

1146
01:42:45,701 --> 01:42:47,787
我也不知道该说什么
I wouldn't say that.

1147
01:42:48,537 --> 01:42:50,539
你中午想吃什么？
What would you like for dinner, huh?

1148
01:42:50,706 --> 01:42:53,876
嗯，洋葱汤，罐装的芦笋
Hey. Onion soup, and canned asparagus...

1149
01:42:54,043 --> 01:42:56,003
我现在真的要回去了
I really should be getting home.

1150
01:42:56,170 --> 01:42:59,131
- 我家里人现在肯定都急疯了　- 你现在还不能离开
- My family'll be flipping by now. - You can't leave yet.

1151
01:42:59,298 --> 01:43:03,719
医生说过需要48个小时，才能把那些东西清除掉
The doctor said it takes 48 hours to get that stuff out of your system.

1152
01:43:04,762 --> 01:43:09,016
那多久才能把那些缠着你的人甩开呢？
How long does it take to get someone you're stuck on out of your system?

1153
01:43:09,183 --> 01:43:12,103
除非他们发明一种专门的抽取泵
If only they'd invent some kind of pump for that.

1154
01:43:12,269 --> 01:43:17,900
库伯利克小姐，我知道你的感受，你认为现在是世界末日，但根本不是你所想的那样
I know how you feel, Miss Kubelik. You think it's the end of the world. But it's not.

1155
01:43:18,067 --> 01:43:20,569
我也经历过一样糟糕的事情
I went through exactly the same thing myself.

1156
01:43:20,736 --> 01:43:22,655
- 你也经历过？　- 是的，当然也不完全一样
- You did? - Well, not exactly the same.

1157
01:43:22,822 --> 01:43:24,573
我想用枪来了结我的一生
I tried to do it with a gun.

1158
01:43:24,740 --> 01:43:27,785
- 为了一个女孩？　- 更糟糕，是为了我最好朋友的老婆
- Over a girl? - Worse. It was the wife of my best friend.

1159
01:43:27,952 --> 01:43:32,957
但是我却疯狂的爱上了她，我知道这是没有结果的，于是想结束这一切
And I was mad about her. But I knew it was hopeless and I decided to end it all.

1160
01:43:33,124 --> 01:43:37,253
我到了一家当铺并买了一把点45自动步枪，然后开车到伊甸公园
I went to a pawnshop and I bought a.45 automatic and I drove up to Eden Park...

1161
01:43:37,420 --> 01:43:39,463
- 你知道辛辛那提吗？　- 不知道
- Do you know Cincinnati? - No, I don't.

1162
01:43:39,630 --> 01:43:42,258
总之，我停好车，把子弹上膛
Anyway, I parked the car and I loaded that gun...

1163
01:43:42,425 --> 01:43:46,762
你读过报纸上说的那些饮弹自尽的文章吧！相信我，事情根本没有那么的简单
You read in the papers that people shoot themselves. Believe me, it's not that easy.

1164
01:43:46,929 --> 01:43:50,599
我知道，那你是怎么做的？这里？这里？还是这里？
I mean, how do you do it? Here? Here? Here?

1165
01:43:51,934 --> 01:43:54,603
- 知道我最后开枪打哪个地方吗？　- 哪里？
- Know where I finally shot myself? - Where?

1166
01:43:54,770 --> 01:43:56,605
- 这里　- 在膝盖上
- Here. - In the knee?!

1167
01:43:56,772 --> 01:43:59,275
是的，我坐在那里，然后在想如何了结
Yeah! I was sittin' there, tryin' to decide.

1168
01:43:59,442 --> 01:44:01,777
因为我违章停车，一个警察走过来
A cop came up because I was illegally parked.

1169
01:44:01,944 --> 01:44:05,281
我想把枪藏在椅子后面，结果枪走火了
I tried to hide the gun under the seat and it went off.

1170
01:44:05,448 --> 01:44:09,076
- 太恐怖了　- 整整一年我都不能弯曲我的膝盖
- That's terrible! - It was a year till I could bend the knee.

1171
01:44:09,243 --> 01:44:12,413
但是后来我三个星期就忘记了那个女孩
But I got over the girl in three weeks.

1172
01:44:13,956 --> 01:44:17,668
她还在辛辛提那有四个小孩，都有20磅重了
Still lives in Cincinnati. Has four kids and gained 20 pounds.

1173
01:44:17,835 --> 01:44:20,212
每个圣诞节还给我送水果蛋糕、
Sends me a fruitcake every Christmas.

1174
01:44:20,379 --> 01:44:22,798
你是不是编出这样的故事让我高兴啊
Are you just making this up to make me feel better?

1175
01:44:22,965 --> 01:44:24,967
当然不是，你看这还有水果蛋糕呢
Of course not! Here's the fruitcake.

1176
01:44:25,134 --> 01:44:27,303
- 你想看我的膝盖吗？　- 不用了，谢谢！
- Do you wanna see my knee? - No, thank you.

1177
01:44:27,470 --> 01:44:30,723
公司的那些家伙可能会奇怪我是怎么知道的
The fellas in the office might get the wrong idea how I found out.

1178
01:44:30,890 --> 01:44:34,977
好了，我来做中餐，水果蛋糕作为饭后的甜点，如何？
Let 'em! Look, I'm gonna cook dinner for us. We'll have fruitcake for dessert.

1179
01:44:35,144 --> 01:44:38,355
你就坐这里休息就够了，今天你的运动已经够多了
You just sit there and rest. You've done enough for today.

1180
01:44:38,522 --> 01:44:41,817
好的，看护大人
- Yes, Nurse. - [Baxter hums opera music]

1181
01:44:55,915 --> 01:44:59,168
- 我能为你做点什么？　- 我找库伯利克小姐
- Can I help you? - I'm lookin' for Miss Kubelik.

1182
01:44:59,335 --> 01:45:04,507
- 我也是，她今天早上没有报到上班　- 她没有吗？谁是这里的主管？
- So am I. She didn't report this morning. - She didn't? Who's in charge here?

1183
01:45:04,673 --> 01:45:08,969
她属于总部下面的行政部，多比奇先生，21楼
That comes under General Office Administration. Mr. Dobisch, 21 st floor.

1184
01:45:09,136 --> 01:45:10,930
谢谢
Thanks.

1185
01:45:13,390 --> 01:45:17,853
我今天带塞维利亚去他的公寓，估计她应该在巴克斯特的房间里.
So I take Sylvia up to the apartment, and guess who he's stashed in the bedroom.

1186
01:45:18,020 --> 01:45:19,271
- 谁？　- 库伯利克
- Who? - Kubelik.

1187
01:45:19,438 --> 01:45:22,525
别开玩笑了，巴德小伙子会和库伯利克有一腿
No kiddin'? Buddy-boy and Kubelik having a little toot?

1188
01:45:22,691 --> 01:45:27,196
也许吧！一个不好的周末，他们今天好像都没有上班
Toot? More like a lost weekend. Neither of 'em showed up for work today.

1189
01:45:27,363 --> 01:45:28,948
擅离职守，对吗？
AWOL, hm?

1190
01:45:29,114 --> 01:45:31,659
尤其让我不爽的就是，他们还拿走了我的香槟
What gripes me is they guzzled my champagne...

1191
01:45:31,825 --> 01:45:35,412
而我和塞尔维亚在高格汉姆博物馆冻得要死
...while Sylvia and I wound up at the Guggenheim Museum.

1192
01:45:37,039 --> 01:45:39,124
- 科比奇先生吗？　- 是的
- Mr. Dobisch? - Yeah.

1193
01:45:40,125 --> 01:45:44,296
我叫卡尔·马塔斯奇卡，我的妹妹叫弗兰·库伯利克，在你们这里开电梯
I'm Karl Matuschka. My sister-in-law runs one of the elevators. Fran Kubelik.

1194
01:45:44,463 --> 01:45:45,923
- 库伯利克小姐？　- 你认识她吗？
- Miss Kubelik? - You know her?

1195
01:45:46,090 --> 01:45:49,927
当然，我们有很多雇员，但我们是一个快乐的幸福大家庭
Of course. We have a lot of employees, but we're one big, happy family.

1196
01:45:50,094 --> 01:45:52,471
她和我们住一起，我妻子克斯弗兰很担心
She lives with us, and my wife's nervous

1197
01:45:52,638 --> 01:45:55,224
因为她已经两天没有回家了
cause Fran hasn't been home for two days.

1198
01:45:55,391 --> 01:45:56,725
那样又如何？
That so?

1199
01:45:56,892 --> 01:45:59,895
于是我们在想你们这里是不是有人知道她的去处
So we wondered if somebody here knew what happened to her.

1200
01:46:00,062 --> 01:46:01,480
我明白
I see.

1201
01:46:01,647 --> 01:46:05,234
你有什么意见，埃尔？我们需要帮助这家伙吗？
What do you think, Al? Can we help the man?

1202
01:46:05,401 --> 01:46:08,779
为什么不呢？我们又不欠巴德什么人情
Why not? We don't owe Buddy-boy anything.

1203
01:46:08,946 --> 01:46:12,491
对，何况巴德最近对我们怎么样，你也是很清楚的
Yeah. What's Buddy-boy done for us lately?

1204
01:46:14,618 --> 01:46:17,037
谁是巴德？
Who is Buddy-boy?

1205
01:46:41,186 --> 01:46:45,024
- 我们需要穿好衣服来吃饭吗？　- 不用，你过来就行了
- Are we dressing for dinner? - No. Just come as you are.

1206
01:46:45,190 --> 01:46:49,361
- 你很会用这球拍　- 你等一下可以看看我反手击球
- You're pretty good with that racket. - You should see my backhand.

1207
01:46:51,363 --> 01:46:54,325
等一下你就可以看到我怎么处理这些肉丸
Wait till you see me serve the meatballs.

1208
01:46:54,491 --> 01:46:58,537
- 我来点蜡烛　- 这将是非常的浪漫、有情调
- Shall I light the candles? - It's a must, gracious livingwise.

1209
01:47:01,790 --> 01:47:03,167
肉丸
 Meatball

1210
01:47:06,962 --> 01:47:08,589
肉丸
 Meatball

1211
01:47:17,640 --> 01:47:20,643
- 你买了一些餐巾　- 最好能够保持一致
- You bought some napkins. - Might as well go all the way.

1212
01:47:24,063 --> 01:47:26,440
你知道的，我曾经像鲁宾逊漂流记中男主角那样生活
You know, I used to live like Robinson Crusoe.

1213
01:47:26,607 --> 01:47:28,817
在八百万人的幸存者中
Shipwrecked, among eight million people.

1214
01:47:28,984 --> 01:47:32,154
有一天我在沙滩上看到了脚印
And then one day I saw a footprint in the sand...

1215
01:47:32,321 --> 01:47:34,365
发现你也在这里
...and there you were.

1216
01:47:35,240 --> 01:47:37,493
太让人兴奋了，两人晚餐
It's a wonderful thing, dinner for two.

1217
01:47:37,660 --> 01:47:41,497
- 你经常一个人吃饭吗？　- 不，有时候我和爱德·苏尔文一起吃
- Do you usually eat alone? - No. Sometimes I eat with Ed Sullivan.

1218
01:47:41,664 --> 01:47:44,416
有时候是戴娜·什莎或者是佩雷·克莫
Or sometimes Dinah Shore or Perry Como.

1219
01:47:44,583 --> 01:47:48,545
另外一个晚上是和梅·韦斯特，她很年轻，干杯
The other night it was Mae West. She was much younger then. Cheers.

1220
01:47:48,712 --> 01:47:51,548
- 干杯　- 我们吃完饭有什么好计划？
- Cheers. - Know what we're gonna do after dinner?

1221
01:47:51,715 --> 01:47:53,759
- 吃菜喽　- 我指那之后
- The dishes. - I mean after that.

1222
01:47:53,926 --> 01:47:56,178
- 什么　- 如果你不喜欢的话不要勉强自己
- What? - You don't have to if you don't want to.

1223
01:47:56,345 --> 01:47:58,722
- 哦，不会的　- 我们再继续打牌吧
- Oh, I don't? - We're gonna finish the gin game.

1224
01:47:58,889 --> 01:48:01,600
保持清醒的头脑
So keep a clear head.

1225
01:48:02,393 --> 01:48:06,397
因为我不想利用你，我昨天在你睡着时候做的事情
Cause I don't wanna take advantage of you, the way I did yesterday in bed.

1226
01:48:06,563 --> 01:48:08,732
- 巴克斯特在吗？　- 在
- Baxter? - Yes.

1227
01:48:17,866 --> 01:48:20,536
弗兰，你和谁在一起呢？你不记得你住在哪里了吗？
What's with you, Fran? Did you forget where you live?

1228
01:48:20,703 --> 01:48:24,373
- 我姐夫，卡尔·马塔斯奇卡　- 你好，马塔斯奇卡先生
- My brother-in-law, Karl Matuschka. - Oh! How do you do, Mr. Matusch...

1229
01:48:24,540 --> 01:48:28,877
- 快穿好衣服，我车在楼下等你　- 等等，我知道你在想什么
- Get dressed. I got the cab downstairs. - Wait. I know what you're thinking, but...

1230
01:48:29,044 --> 01:48:31,797
你做什么不关我的事情，你已经超过21岁了
It's none of my business what you do. You're over 21.

1231
01:48:31,964 --> 01:48:35,551
- 但是你姐姐还认为你是一个小女孩　- 我们只是在这里吃饭
- But your sister thinks you're a lady. - All we were gonna do was eat!

1232
01:48:35,718 --> 01:48:38,178
如果不是这里有一位女士在场的话，我会痛扁你一顿的
If there wasn't a lady present, I'd clobber you.

1233
01:48:38,345 --> 01:48:41,265
好的，卡尔，我去穿衣服
All right, Karl! I'll get dressed.

1234
01:48:50,441 --> 01:48:52,568
来一杯马提尼如何？
Want a martini?

1235
01:48:56,488 --> 01:49:00,409
来一些我做的意大利肉酱面？
How about some spaghetti with meat sauce that I cooked myself?

1236
01:49:05,914 --> 01:49:08,751
你姐夫实在太恐怖了
Your sister-in-law sure is terrific.

1237
01:49:11,920 --> 01:49:16,425
如果他在马路上开车，肯定会害死其他司机的
It must be murder drivin' a cab in New York with the cross-town traffic.

1238
01:49:20,929 --> 01:49:22,931
嗨，巴克斯特，病人现在情况怎么样？
Hi, Baxter. How's the patient?

1239
01:49:23,098 --> 01:49:25,100
哦，我还好，医生
Oh, uh... I'm fine, Doc.

1240
01:49:25,267 --> 01:49:27,311
不是你，是库伯利克小姐
Not you. Miss Kubelik.

1241
01:49:28,020 --> 01:49:32,941
- 库伯利克小姐发生什么事情了？　- 他是马塔斯奇卡先生，一个出租车司机
- What's the matter with Miss Kubelik? - This is Mr. Matuschka. He's... got a cab.

1242
01:49:33,108 --> 01:49:35,527
- 弗兰生病了吗？　- 没有，出了一点小意外
- Fran been sick? - No. Just a little accident.

1243
01:49:35,694 --> 01:49:39,615
- 他的话是什么意思，意外？　- 哦，是这样的，这些事情一直都在发生
- What does he mean, accident? - Well... these things happen all the time.

1244
01:49:39,782 --> 01:49:41,909
什么事情？你究竟当的什么医生？
What things? What kind of a doctor are you?

1245
01:49:42,076 --> 01:49:45,245
不是什么，他只是给她打了一针，然后洗了一下胃
Not that kind! He just gave her a shot, pumped out her stomach.

1246
01:49:45,412 --> 01:49:48,624
- 为什么？　- 我吃了安眠药，不过我现在已经没事了
- What for? - I took sleeping pills. But I'm fine now.

1247
01:49:48,791 --> 01:49:51,293
- 你为什么吃安眠药？　- 因为我
- Why'd you take sleeping pills? - On account of me.

1248
01:49:51,460 --> 01:49:53,462
你？
You?

1249
01:49:53,629 --> 01:49:55,464
能有其他人吗？
Who else?

1250
01:50:00,302 --> 01:50:02,387
放开他
Leave him alone!

1251
01:50:04,723 --> 01:50:08,060
哦，你这个傻瓜，太傻了
Oh, you fool. You damn fool.

1252
01:50:10,145 --> 01:50:13,315
- 快走，弗兰　- 巴克斯特先生，再见
- [Karl] Come on, Fran. - Goodbye, Mr. Baxter.

1253
01:50:19,196 --> 01:50:21,323
再见，医生
Goodbye, Doctor.

1254
01:50:23,158 --> 01:50:27,996
好了，我不想幸灾乐祸，不过你刚才确实很有勇气承担责任
Well, I don't wanna gloat, but just between us, you had it coming to you.

1255
01:50:30,207 --> 01:50:33,085
你明天就会有一个黑眼圈
You're gonna have a shiner tomorrow.

1256
01:50:33,252 --> 01:50:35,170
让我拿一下包
Let me get my bag.

1257
01:50:37,214 --> 01:50:39,216
不用担心，医生
Don't bother, Doc.

1258
01:50:39,383 --> 01:50:41,468
伤的不是很厉害
It doesn't hurt a bit.

1259
01:51:03,240 --> 01:51:05,534
舍尔爵克先生的办公室吗？我是CC·巴克斯特
Mr. Sheldrake's office? This is C.C. Baxter.

1260
01:51:05,701 --> 01:51:08,912
请告诉他我想现在就见他，有很重要的事情
Please tell him I'd like to come up and see him. It's important.

1261
01:51:09,079 --> 01:51:11,206
请问你能打回来吗？
Will you call me back, please?

1262
01:51:13,917 --> 01:51:17,045
舍尔爵克先生，我有好消息要告诉你
Mr. Sheldrake, I've got good news for you.

1263
01:51:18,213 --> 01:51:20,257
所有的麻烦都结束了
All your troubles are over.

1264
01:51:21,425 --> 01:51:24,303
我想我可以帮你摆脱库伯利克小姐
I'm gonna take Miss Kubelik off your hands.

1265
01:51:25,095 --> 01:51:27,598
事实就是我喜欢她
The plain fact is, I love her.

1266
01:51:28,473 --> 01:51:31,059
我想你是第一个知道的人
I thought you should be the first to know.

1267
01:51:31,226 --> 01:51:34,062
毕竟，你不喜欢她，而我却喜欢
After all, you don't really want her, and I do.

1268
01:51:34,229 --> 01:51:38,317
虽然这听起来有些专横，但是她需要像我这样的人来照顾
And though it may sound presumptuous, she needs somebody like me.

1269
01:51:38,483 --> 01:51:41,904
于是我想我应该是最适合的人选
So I think it would be best all around.

1270
01:51:42,070 --> 01:51:43,488
这样才能解决问题
Solutionwise.

1271
01:51:43,655 --> 01:51:44,907
喂？
Yes?

1272
01:51:45,073 --> 01:51:47,200
我马上上来
I'll be right up.

1273
01:51:47,367 --> 01:51:50,746
舍尔爵克先生，我有好消息要告诉你
Mr. Sheldrake, I've got good news for you.

1274
01:51:50,913 --> 01:51:52,956
所有的麻烦都结束了
All your troubles are over.

1275
01:51:57,252 --> 01:51:59,421
19楼
19.

1276
01:51:59,588 --> 01:52:03,258
- 嗨，巴德小伙子，你怎么了？　- 被门撞到了吗？
- Hi, Buddy-boy. What happened to you? - Hit by a swinging door?

1277
01:52:03,425 --> 01:52:06,303
- 或者是黄色的出租车撞到了　- 那个家伙可能已经揍了他
- Or a yellow cab? - That guy really must've belted him.

1278
01:52:06,470 --> 01:52:09,598
是的，你看他已经心不在焉，自言自语
Yeah. He's punchy. Talking to himself.

1279
01:52:09,765 --> 01:52:11,266
27楼
27.

1280
01:52:11,433 --> 01:52:13,852
这两天她住在我的公寓里
Those two days she spent in the apartment...

1281
01:52:14,019 --> 01:52:16,980
才让我意识到我原来多么的孤独
...made me realize how lonely I'd been before.

1282
01:52:17,147 --> 01:52:20,651
但是多亏了你，让我有足够的收入来娶她
But, thanks to you, I'm in a financial position to marry her.

1283
01:52:20,817 --> 01:52:23,820
如果我能和她的家人协商好的话
If I can ever square things with her family.

1284
01:52:23,987 --> 01:52:26,448
早上好，CC·巴克斯特先生
Good morning. C.C. Baxter.

1285
01:52:30,369 --> 01:52:32,454
- 他已经到了　- 让他进来
- Mr. Baxter is here. - Send him in.

1286
01:52:34,665 --> 01:52:37,542
舍尔爵克先生，我有好消息要告诉你
Mr. Sheldrake, I've got good news for you.

1287
01:52:37,709 --> 01:52:39,795
巴克斯特，我也有好消息告诉你
And I've got good news for you, Baxter.

1288
01:52:39,962 --> 01:52:42,297
所有的问题都迎刃而解了。先生？
- All your troubles are over. - Sir?

1289
01:52:42,631 --> 01:52:45,801
我知道你很担心库伯利克小姐，现在你不用管了
I know how worried you were about Miss Kubelik. Stop worrying.

1290
01:52:45,968 --> 01:52:48,804
我将要把她从你那里接过来
I'm going to take her off your hands.

1291
01:52:48,971 --> 01:52:51,807
- 从我这里接过去　- 很对
- You're gonna take her off my hands? - That's right.

1292
01:52:51,974 --> 01:52:54,476
我已经从家里搬出来了
I've moved out of the house.

1293
01:52:55,394 --> 01:52:58,355
目前打算住在镇上，住在运动俱乐部
I'm gonna be staying in town, at the Athletic Club.

1294
01:52:58,522 --> 01:53:01,483
- 你和你妻子离婚了？　- 如果你非要知道的话，我告诉你，我炒掉我的秘书
- You left your wife. - If you must know, I fired my secretary.

1295
01:53:01,650 --> 01:53:06,446
我秘书告诉了我的妻子，我妻子炒掉我，对我而言真是一个重大的不幸
My secretary got to my wife, and my wife fired me. Ain't that a kick in the head?

1296
01:53:06,613 --> 01:53:08,156
是的
Yeah.

1297
01:53:08,323 --> 01:53:10,242
巴克斯特，你有什么好消息可以告诉我的
Now what's your news, Baxter?

1298
01:53:12,369 --> 01:53:16,039
是关于库伯利克小姐的，她现在完全康复，然后回家去了
It's about Miss Kubelik. She's feeling all right again so she went home.

1299
01:53:16,206 --> 01:53:19,334
很好，我没有忘记你为我做的事情
Swell. And don't think I've forgotten what you did for me.

1300
01:53:19,501 --> 01:53:21,545
这边来，巴克斯特
This way, Baxter.

1301
01:53:24,923 --> 01:53:27,342
坐下，大小合适吗？
Sit down. Try it on for size.

1302
01:53:28,343 --> 01:53:30,846
- 喜欢吗？这里都是你的　- 我的？
- You like? It's all yours. - Mine?

1303
01:53:31,013 --> 01:53:36,184
我的助理已经被轮调到丹佛的办公室，由你来接替他的位置
My assistant has been shifted to the Denver office and you're taking his place.

1304
01:53:36,351 --> 01:53:38,770
怎么了，有什么事情吗？你看起来好像并不很兴奋
What's the matter? You don't seem very excited.

1305
01:53:38,937 --> 01:53:43,191
哦，只是很多事情变化太快了，让我都有些无所适从
Well, it's just that so many things have been happening so fast.

1306
01:53:43,358 --> 01:53:46,069
我很高兴，特别为库伯利克小姐高兴
I'm very pleased. Especially for Miss Kubelik.

1307
01:53:46,236 --> 01:53:51,199
我觉得她就是那种合适嫁给一些人的女孩
I think she's the kind of girl that definitely ought to be married to... someone.

1308
01:53:51,366 --> 01:53:56,872
当然，当然，首先我要处理好财产问题，然后再花六个星期的时间在雷诺休息。
Sure, sure. But first the property has to be settled. Then it takes six weeks in Reno.

1309
01:53:57,039 --> 01:53:59,875
同时我也要好好地享受一下单身汉的快乐
Meanwhile I'm going to enjoy being a bachelor for a while.

1310
01:54:00,042 --> 01:54:03,462
对了，巴克斯特，你可以在经理餐厅吃饭了
Oh, Baxter, you now can have lunch in the executive dining room.

1311
01:54:03,628 --> 01:54:06,256
这是担任这一工作的特权之一
That's one of the privileges that goes with this job.

1312
01:54:06,423 --> 01:54:11,011
你还可以公费报销一些项目，使用经理盥洗室
You also get a nice little expense account, use of the executive washroom...

1313
01:54:11,178 --> 01:54:13,555
嘿，巴克斯特，你怎么了？
Say, what happened to you, Baxter?

1314
01:54:13,722 --> 01:54:16,475
- 我也备受打击　- 哦
- I got kicked in the head too. - Oh?

1315
01:54:37,579 --> 01:54:39,623
晚安，巴克斯特先生
Good evening, Mr. Baxter.

1316
01:54:39,790 --> 01:54:41,249
哦
Oh.

1317
01:54:41,416 --> 01:54:44,169
库伯利克小姐，你现在感觉如何？
Miss Kubelik. How are you feeling?

1318
01:54:44,336 --> 01:54:47,005
- 我很好，你的眼睛怎么样了？　- 哦，没事
- I feel fine. How's your eye? - Oh, fine.

1319
01:54:47,172 --> 01:54:49,966
- 公寓现在怎么样　- 还是老样子，什么都没变
- How are things at the apartment? - Nothing's changed.

1320
01:54:50,133 --> 01:54:53,136
- 我们那个牌局还没有打完呢　- 我知道
- We never did finish that gin game. - I know.

1321
01:54:54,805 --> 01:54:57,140
我想你已经知道舍尔爵克的事情了吧
I suppose you heard about Mr. Sheldrake.

1322
01:54:57,307 --> 01:54:59,851
和他夫人离婚？对，我很为他高兴
Leaving his wife? Yeah. I'm very happy for you.

1323
01:55:00,018 --> 01:55:02,604
- 我从来没有想过他会做这件事情　- 我早就告诉过你了
- I never thought he'd do it. - I told you all along.

1324
01:55:02,771 --> 01:55:06,233
- 你对舍尔爵克先生有一些误会　- 我想是的吧
- You were wrong about Mr. Sheldrake. - I guess so.

1325
01:55:06,400 --> 01:55:08,401
你对我也有一些误会
You were wrong about me too.

1326
01:55:08,568 --> 01:55:11,696
就是关于谁泡谁和谁被泡的问题
What you said about those who take and those who get took.

1327
01:55:11,863 --> 01:55:15,033
舍尔爵克先生没有利用我，我在玩他，明白吗？
Mr. Sheldrake wasn't using me. I was using him. See?

1328
01:55:15,200 --> 01:55:19,663
上个月我在19楼的861号桌子，现在我在27楼了
Last month I was at desk 861 on the 19th floor. Now I'm on the 27th floor.

1329
01:55:19,830 --> 01:55:21,832
套间的办公室，还有三扇窗尸
A paneled office, three windows.

1330
01:55:21,998 --> 01:55:25,001
因此一切都发展得很好，我们各得其所
So it all worked out fine. We're both getting what we wanted.

1331
01:55:25,168 --> 01:55:28,046
是的，你能陪我到地铁吗？
Yes. Will you walk me to the subway?

1332
01:55:28,213 --> 01:55:33,969
不了，谢谢，我告诉你，我今天晚上有一个很重要的约会
No, thank you. Well, I... To tell you the truth, I have this heavy date for tonight.

1333
01:55:37,389 --> 01:55:40,725
- 你不和舍尔爵克先生会面吗？　- 不，你知道人言可畏的
- Aren't you meeting Mr. Sheldrake? - No. You know how people talk.

1334
01:55:40,892 --> 01:55:46,148
我决定在所有事情都解决好之前不和他见面，也就是等他离婚之后
I decided it was best not to see each other until everything was settled, divorcewise.

1335
01:55:46,314 --> 01:55:48,400
明智之举
That's very wise.

1336
01:55:49,484 --> 01:55:51,987
- 晚安，巴克斯特先生　- 晚安
- Good night, Mr. Baxter. - Good night.

1337
01:56:27,981 --> 01:56:31,359
- 巴克斯特，你能到我这里来一下吗？　- 好的，舍尔爵克先生
- Baxter, could you step in here a minute? - Yes, Mr. Sheldrake.

1338
01:56:31,526 --> 01:56:33,570
- 这是你要的东西　- 非常感谢
- There you are. - Much obliged.

1339
01:56:35,405 --> 01:56:41,203
这是员工离职率，为37%，女性员工结婚率为22%...
Here are the figures on staff turnover. 37% of females leave to get married and 22%...

1340
01:56:41,369 --> 01:56:44,289
巴克斯特，你工作太辛苦了，今天是除夕，放松点
Baxter, you work too hard. It's New Year's Eve. Relax!

1341
01:56:44,456 --> 01:56:47,417
- 是的，先生　- 我想你今天晚上应该庆祝一番吧
- Yes, sir. - I suppose you'll be celebrating tonight.

1342
01:56:47,584 --> 01:56:49,753
- 那是自然　- 我准备约库伯利克小姐出来
- Naturally. - I'm taking Miss Kubelik out.

1343
01:56:49,920 --> 01:56:51,922
- 我想和她促膝畅谈　- 我明白
- I finally talked her into it. - I see.

1344
01:56:52,088 --> 01:56:56,426
唯一的问题是我还住在运动俱乐部，那里全是男的，不太方便
The only thing is, I'm staying at the Athletic Club and it's strictly stag, so...

1345
01:56:56,593 --> 01:56:58,762
如果你不介意的话？
If you don't mind?

1346
01:56:59,554 --> 01:57:03,058
- 不介意什么　- 你知道的，你公寓的钥匙
- Don't mind what? - You know my key to your apartment?

1347
01:57:03,225 --> 01:57:06,394
就是我们被库伯利克小姐吓了一跳的地方
When we had that little scare about Miss Kubelik...

1348
01:57:06,561 --> 01:57:10,565
- 我早就忘记了　- 非常聪明
...I threw it out the window of the train. - Very clever.

1349
01:57:10,732 --> 01:57:13,068
所以现在我要借用你的钥匙
So now I'll have to borrow your key.

1350
01:57:14,528 --> 01:57:17,322
- 不好意思，舍尔爵克先生　- 不好意思，为什么？
- Sorry, Mr. Sheldrake. - What do you mean, sorry?

1351
01:57:17,489 --> 01:57:19,866
你不能带任何人再到我的公寓来
You're not bringing anybody to my apartment.

1352
01:57:20,033 --> 01:57:24,371
- 不是别人，是库伯利克小姐　- 她更不行
- It's not just anybody. It's Miss Kubelik. - Especially not Miss Kubelik.

1353
01:57:24,537 --> 01:57:27,791
- 我再问你一遍？　- 不行
- How's that again? - No key.

1354
01:57:29,626 --> 01:57:34,214
巴克斯特，我把你调到我身边是因为我觉得你是一个非常年轻聪明的孩子
Baxter, I picked you for my team because I thought you were a bright young man.

1355
01:57:34,381 --> 01:57:37,801
你知道你在干什么吗？这对我没什么，但是对你影响有多大？
Do you realize what you're doing? Not to me, but to yourself?

1356
01:57:37,968 --> 01:57:41,304
一般来说你要花很多时间才能到27楼来工作
Normally it takes years to work your way up to the 27th floor.

1357
01:57:41,471 --> 01:57:44,474
但是可能只要30秒钟你就可以被扫地出门
But it only takes 30 seconds to be out on the street again.

1358
01:57:44,641 --> 01:57:47,269
- 你懂吗？　- 我懂
- You dig? - I dig.

1359
01:57:48,395 --> 01:57:50,480
那你现在应该怎么办呢？
So what's it going to be?

1360
01:57:57,237 --> 01:58:00,365
- 这样才对　- 谢谢，先生
- Now you're being bright. - Thank you, sir.

1361
01:58:17,757 --> 01:58:20,427
- 巴克斯特，你拿错钥匙给我了　- 没有
- Baxter, you gave me the wrong key. - No, I didn't.

1362
01:58:20,594 --> 01:58:23,221
但这是经理盥洗室的钥匙
But this is the key to the executive washroom.

1363
01:58:23,388 --> 01:58:27,142
没错，我不再需要它了，因为我已经要离开这里
That's right. I won't be needing it because I'm all washed up around here.

1364
01:58:27,309 --> 01:58:30,687
- 你傻了吗？　- 你要听我的话
- What's gotten into you? - Just following doctor's orders.

1365
01:58:30,854 --> 01:58:35,066
我想做一个人，知道什么意思吗？一个堂堂正正的人
I've decided to become a mensch. Know what that means? A human being.

1366
01:58:35,233 --> 01:58:39,154
- 等等，巴克斯特　- 这种逢迎拍马的老伎俩没用了
- Now hold on, Baxter. - The old payola won't work any more.

1367
01:58:39,321 --> 01:58:41,406
再见，舍尔爵克先生
Goodbye, Mr. Sheldrake.

1368
01:59:16,983 --> 01:59:20,904
- 我们有一个晚会，没有冰了，你可以拿过来一些吗？　- 好的，医生
- We're having a party and ran out of ice. - Sure, Doc.

1369
01:59:21,071 --> 01:59:23,156
在除夕之夜你怎么一个人呢
How come you're alone on New Year's Eve?

1370
01:59:23,323 --> 01:59:25,241
哦，我要做一些事情
Well, I got things to do.

1371
01:59:25,408 --> 01:59:29,579
- 这是什么，你在收拾行李？　- 是的，我准备离开这里
- What's this? You're packing? - Yeah. I'm giving up the apartment.

1372
01:59:29,746 --> 01:59:31,581
你要到哪里发展呢？
Where are you moving to?

1373
01:59:31,748 --> 01:59:34,751
我不知道，不过有一点可以确认，就是离开这里
I don't know. All I know is I gotta get outta this place.

1374
01:59:34,918 --> 01:59:36,920
巴克斯特，看到你要走，我很难过
Sorry to lose you, Baxter.

1375
01:59:37,087 --> 01:59:41,800
我？哦，我的身体，不要担心，我还会捐给大学的，我在写申请
Me? Oh, my body. Don't worry, it'll go to the university, Doc. I'll put it in writing.

1376
01:59:41,966 --> 01:59:45,136
- 需要香槟吗？　- 我们不喝酒
- Could you use some champagne? - Booze we don't need.

1377
01:59:45,303 --> 01:59:47,097
嘿，为什么不和我们一起玩呢
Say, why don't you join us?

1378
01:59:47,263 --> 01:59:52,227
我们有两个脑外科医生，一个直肠病学家，三个从贝利弗来的护士
We got two brain surgeons, a proctologist and three nurses from Bellevue.

1379
01:59:52,394 --> 01:59:54,312
不用，谢谢，我现在没心情
No, thanks. I don't feel like it.

1380
01:59:54,479 --> 01:59:58,692
万一以后我们碰不到面了，我怎么偿还你帮我照顾那个女孩的人情
In case I don't see you again, how much do I owe you for taking care of that girl?

1381
01:59:58,858 --> 02:00:02,695
不要想了，我没当自己是医生，我只是在尽一个邻居的义务
Forget it. I didn't do it as a doctor. I did it as a neighbor.

1382
02:00:02,862 --> 02:00:05,573
顺便问一句，她现在怎么样了？
By the way, whatever happened to her?

1383
02:00:06,825 --> 02:00:09,786
你知道我和女孩如何谈得了！来也匆匆，去也匆匆
You know me with girls. Easy come, easy go.

1384
02:00:09,953 --> 02:00:12,664
- 再见，医生　- 新年快乐
- Goodbye, Doc. - Happy New Year.

1385
02:00:56,082 --> 02:00:58,460
不好意思，我打了太久的电话，一切都准备好了
Sorry I took so long on the phone. We're all set.

1386
02:00:58,626 --> 02:01:01,045
- 干什么？　- 我租了一辆车，我们一点的时候用
- For what? - I rented a car. It'll be here at one.

1387
02:01:01,212 --> 02:01:04,048
- 我们开车到亚特兰大　- 亚特兰大？
- We're driving to Atlantic City. - Atlantic City?

1388
02:01:04,215 --> 02:01:08,803
我知道太远了，可是在除夕之夜纽约的酒店根本没有空房间
I know it's a drag, but you can't find a hotel room in town on New Year's Eve.

1389
02:01:09,804 --> 02:01:12,640
辞旧迎新
Ring out the old year, ring in the new.

1390
02:01:12,807 --> 02:01:15,059
我们来狂欢吧！
Ring-a-ding-ding.

1391
02:01:15,518 --> 02:01:18,855
我也不想这样的，这都是巴克斯特的错
I didn't plan it this way. It's Baxter's fault.

1392
02:01:19,022 --> 02:01:19,981
巴克斯特？
Baxter?

1393
02:01:20,148 --> 02:01:23,651
他不愿意给我公寓的钥匙
He wouldn't give me the key to the apartment.

1394
02:01:23,818 --> 02:01:26,362
- 他不愿意？　- 是的，他离开我，辞职了
- He wouldn't? - No. He just walked out on me. Quit.

1395
02:01:26,529 --> 02:01:29,616
抛弃了在我身边的这么好的工作
Threw that big, fat job right in my face.

1396
02:01:30,992 --> 02:01:35,038
神经病，废物一个，毕竟他的一切都是我给的
- The nerve. - The little punk. After all I did for him.

1397
02:01:35,205 --> 02:01:39,501
还说我再也不能带任何人到他的公寓，特别是库伯利克小姐不行
Said I couldn't bring anybody to the apartment, especially not Miss Kubelik.

1398
02:01:39,667 --> 02:01:42,462
那么他为什么要和你作对呢？
What's he got against you, anyway?

1399
02:01:42,629 --> 02:01:48,551
我不知道，也许这是最好的解决办法，就像粉碎的小甜饼一样
I don't know. I guess that's the way it crumbles, cookiewise.

1400
02:01:50,553 --> 02:01:53,014
你在说什么
What are you talking about?

1401
02:01:54,015 --> 02:01:57,477
我想为你把它拼出来，可是我不会
I'd spell it out for you, only I can't spell.

1402
02:02:02,440 --> 02:02:07,487
# Should auld acquaintance be forgot
Should auld acquaintance be forgot

1403
02:02:07,654 --> 02:02:12,617
# And never brought to mind…
And never brought to mind...

1404
02:02:13,910 --> 02:02:15,995
新年快乐，弗兰
Happy New Year, Fran.

1405
02:02:18,039 --> 02:02:22,460
# And days of auld lang syne
And days of auld lang syne

1406
02:02:23,294 --> 02:02:28,424
# For auld lang syne, my dear
For auld lang syne, my dear

1407
02:02:28,591 --> 02:02:33,555
# For auld lang syne
For auld lang syne

1408
02:02:33,721 --> 02:02:38,935
# We'll drink a cup of kindness yet
We'll drink a cup of kindness yet

1409
02:02:39,102 --> 02:02:44,732
# For auld lang syne
For auld lang syne

1410
02:02:56,452 --> 02:02:58,538
弗兰？
Fran?

1411
02:02:59,789 --> 02:03:01,874
你跑哪里去了，弗兰？
Where are you, Fran?

1412
02:03:19,976 --> 02:03:22,061
巴克斯特先生
Mr. Baxter!

1413
02:03:22,312 --> 02:03:23,521
巴克斯特先生

1414
02:03:23,855 --> 02:03:26,899
巴克斯特先生！巴克斯特先生
Mr. Baxter! Mr. Baxter!

1415
02:03:29,861 --> 02:03:31,154
天啊！
Oh!

1416
02:03:31,321 --> 02:03:34,407
- 你还好吗？　- 我很好
- Are you all right? - I'm fine.

1417
02:03:34,574 --> 02:03:37,076
你确认吗？你膝盖怎么样？
Are you sure? How's your knee?

1418
02:03:37,785 --> 02:03:39,871
浑身上下都没有问题
I'm fine all over.

1419
02:03:41,873 --> 02:03:45,335
- 介意我进来吗？　- 当然不
- Mind if I come in? - Of course not.

1420
02:03:49,047 --> 02:03:51,132
我给你拿一只杯子
Let me get another glass.

1421
02:03:54,052 --> 02:03:56,137
- 你准备去哪里？　- 天知道
- Where are you going? - Who knows?

1422
02:03:56,304 --> 02:03:59,599
找另外一个邻居，到另外一个城市，再找另外一份工作
Another neighborhood, another town, another job.

1423
02:03:59,766 --> 02:04:02,060
我现在一个人过
I'm on my own.

1424
02:04:02,226 --> 02:04:04,312
太有趣了，我也是
That's funny. So am I.

1425
02:04:05,480 --> 02:04:07,732
你把牌放哪里去了？
What'd you do with the cards?

1426
02:04:07,899 --> 02:04:09,984
在那里
In there.

1427
02:04:21,287 --> 02:04:23,289
那舍尔爵克先生呢
What about Mr. Sheldrake?

1428
02:04:23,456 --> 02:04:26,584
我会每个圣诞节送他一个水果蛋糕
I'm gonna send him a fruitcake every Christmas.

1429
02:04:29,003 --> 02:04:31,089
切牌
Cut.

1430
02:04:32,715 --> 02:04:34,801
我爱你，库伯利克小姐
I love you, Miss Kubelik.

1431
02:04:35,301 --> 02:04:37,095
3
Three.

1432
02:04:37,261 --> 02:04:38,429
皇后(Q)
Queen.

1433
02:04:38,596 --> 02:04:42,642
你听到我说什么吗？库伯利克小姐，我绝对喜欢你
Did you hear what I said, Miss Kubelik? I absolutely adore you.

1434
02:04:45,269 --> 02:04:47,355
闭嘴，我们打牌
Shut up and deal.
